title: Must See This Beautiful 2-Bedroom, Third Level, Corner Unit
posting_body: ['A NEW STYLE OF LIVING', 'Welcome to Aspen Creek Apartment Homes, where we invite you to experience a friendly relaxed retreat tucked away in the middle of a vibrant, dynamic, small city thriving in the western shadow of Mt. Rainier.', 'With a wide range of resort-style amenities from heated pool to sun deck to coffee bar, our Puyallup apartments offer the perfect blend of in-home privacy, communal camaraderie, and caring customer service.', 'Come see for yourself why our pet friendly community is the right choice for you!', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 890 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Ceiling Fans', '- Refrigerator', '- Washer and Dryer', '- Beautiful Views', '- Window Coverings', '- Disposal', '- Breakfast Bar', '- Large Closets', '- Cable or Satellite Ready', '- Fully Equipped Kitchens', '- Private Patio or Balcony', '- Microwave', '- Additional Storage', '- Carpeting', 'Community Amenities', '- Clubhouse', '- Spa/Hot Tub', '- On-Site Maintenance', '- Package Receiving', '- Close to Bus Stop', '- Pool', '- Short Term Lease', '- Fitness Center', '- Sun Deck', '- Pet Stations', '- Off Leash Dog Park', '- Carport', '- Two Playgrounds', '- Coffee Bar (with complimentary coffee)', 'Pet Policy', 'Pets - Max 2 allowed, One time Fee $250.00, Rent $35.00, Deposit $250.00', 'Cats - allowed,', 'Dogs - allowed', 'Income Requirements:', 'Three times the rent', 'Office Hours', 'MON-FRI: 09:00 AM-06:00 PM', 'SATURDAY: 9:00 AM-06:00 PM', 'Aspen Creek Apartments', '12724 104TH AVENUE CT E, Puyallup, WA, 98374', 'Disclaimer: Please be aware of scams on Craigslist.', 'It is our practice never to require someone to complete a credit application or provide personal credit information before touring an apartment home.', 'Rent is based on lease term selected.', 'Please contact office for more details.', 'Prices subject to change.', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', '8xqxOrge #weloveyourpets #lovewhereyoulive #bestinpuyallup']
